You need to read more books.

574
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,630
Kay, could I have just a word?

575
00:29:58,630 --> 00:30:00,870
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHATTERING)</font>

576
00:30:00,870 --> 00:30:01,910
Um...

577
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,940
Everything all right?

578
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,980
- Marg okay?
