684
00:34:58,440 --> 00:35:01,040
Harder for you, I imagine.

685
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,740
No.

686
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,240
Why?

687
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:06,570
These were your people...

688
00:35:06,580 --> 00:35:09,980
McNamara and Kennedy
and Johnson.

