694
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,320
Oh, well, he just wanted
the paper to endorse.

695
00:35:22,330 --> 00:35:23,590
Yes, but my point is

696
00:35:23,590 --> 00:35:25,560
you had Steve and Bill
waiting at home.

697
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:26,760
- You had houseguests...
