701
00:35:31,270 --> 00:35:32,370
Yet you jumped
on Air Force One,

702
00:35:32,370 --> 00:35:33,440
spent the weekend...

703
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:34,500
I did not jump.

704
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,770
...swimming
and speed-boating...

705
00:35:35,770 --> 00:35:37,340
You and Luvie Pearson
said I had to go!

706
00:35:37,340 --> 00:35:38,910
...with Lyndon
and Lady Bird.

707
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:46,680
It's hard to say...

